{"tid":675461,"cid":11,"subCid":0,"title":"如果陳百祥（阿叻）生係呢個年代，佢會做到幾成功？","createTime":"2018-05-23T13:50:38.000Z","updateTime":"2018-05-24T05:05:19.000Z","uid":28786,"like":59,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":19,"replies":[{"pid":"0501e08b433093b3919ce6ffb4d88a6f734a1cc0","tid":675461,"uid":28786,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-05-23T13:50:38.000Z","msg":"條友中學畢業<br />\n冇樣，唔識唱歌，冇演技，冇星味，冇才華，冇品，冇風度<br />\n總括黎講就係冇實力，死好命以前做下小醜都比佢紅到，做埋大台元老主持<br />\n如果生係呢個年代入tvb，就算佢點努力都好，都大把人做主持做得好過佢，連龜頭bob都不如，只係佢口中講唔努力既廢青<br />\n<br />\n講到最尾我都係想講佢有咩資格批評香港人同埋我地班後生，只靠死好命上到位就成日串串貢<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/fuck.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d35673fb892c7540c6e04d5d8bb3410d9b32a713","tid":675461,"uid":130895,"like":0,"dislike":7,"score":-7,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2018-05-23T13:55:49.000Z","msg":"第二個王祖藍"},{"pid":"b2ff7d112356031b8f0a493f3f7472ef595fd16f","tid":675461,"uid":164920,"like":42,"dislike":0,"score":42,"quote":{"pid":"d35673fb892c7540c6e04d5d8bb3410d9b32a713","tid":675461,"uid":130895,"like":0,"dislike":7,"score":-7,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2018-05-23T13:55:49.000Z","msg":"第二個王祖藍"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-05-23T14:31:41.000Z","msg":"王祖藍至少都叫演藝學院first hon"},{"pid":"ad59c4b8e8025680126ae94c354906cd87071b2c","tid":675461,"uid":88123,"like":7,"dislike":0,"score":7,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-05-23T14:44:55.000Z","msg":"可以係馬會執馬屎啩"},{"pid":"5ec0759dd3c4f24d1726452a309ff348e05fd04a","tid":675461,"uid":42909,"like":18,"dislike":1,"score":17,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-05-23T14:48:51.000Z","msg":"只係一個轉數快啲，但講野無内涵既連登仔<br />\n但為求上位，會走去奶啲有權有勢、共產黨鞋㡳。"},{"pid":"fd9e7d6c2b2c91f974cd07f5cb8899203d1af9dd","tid":675461,"uid":55458,"like":11,"dislike":0,"score":11,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-05-23T14:49:16.000Z","msg":"比世界上最醜嘅女人強姦"},{"pid":"99bccc4153861cf8ab616e5cdd61eb2eb36fa0e7","tid":675461,"uid":174601,"like":7,"dislike":0,"score":7,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-05-23T14:49:44.000Z","msg":"唯唯咁既level"},{"pid":"36ee662b17adc35a9190a4e450f17290f0043194","tid":